{"title":"小红帽脱险记１１","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记１１"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正放了心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子跑到了破茅屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子抓住了破柴门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柴门太老又太破，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子被他的黑手打开了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柴门太矮又太小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子他的黑毛脚就伸进门槛来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他正在弯着腰，缩着身体向里钻……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从门角里闪出了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小铁匠和小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个拿着铁锤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当头一锤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个拿着钢刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当胸一刀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎哟——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来不及说话来不及叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上带着一个洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸口带着一把刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚跌跌的就往外逃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你逃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你逃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你逃到哪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你逃到海角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们追到海角！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你逃到天涯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们追到天涯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了无数的小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和他们做的梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们一定要捉住你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了无数的小铁匠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和他们妈妈的手爸爸的腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们一定要消灭你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作恶作够了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"害人害满了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还没有逃到山脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就一个筋斗倒在路边了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一动也不能动了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的眼睛永远闭不拢了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的爪子牙齿再也没有用了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你脱险了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小铁匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你胜利了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽抱着小铁匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小铁匠抱着小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面跳，一面唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面唱，又一面笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜红的太阳出来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜红的太阳出来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳那么亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳照四方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳那么红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家好做工。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小黄狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕，你少贪小利快来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来放哨，来打猎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大白马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕，你少发牢骚快来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来拖车，来耕地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老蜜蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕，你少唱山歌快来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来采花，来酿蜜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快来呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳是我们的！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快来吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快来呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界是我们的！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么多！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着小铁匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一面唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小铁匠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮呀当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扭呀摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到哪里去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑到哪里去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去造一座大花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去造一座大彩桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九，五月十日初稿完，八月二十五日改成。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}